<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
  <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>
    Our records indicate that you had a reservation for today, <%= Date.today.strftime("%A, %d %B %Y")  %> at <%= @start_time.partition(' ').last %> going to <%= @reservation.site.title %>
    and haven't yet completed a Vehicle Report. If you didn't use the vehicle please let us know so that the reservation can be canceled. 
    If you did use the vehicle, please go to reservation to <%= link_to "to fill out", reservation_url(@reservation) %> the Vehicle Report now.
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you,<br>
      Your <%= @reservation.program.unit.name %> RideShare Team
    </p>
    <p>
      You can email <%= @unit_email %> or call the office at: <%= @contact_phone %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Visit <%= link_to "LSA RideShare", all_root_url %> to view, modify, or cancel reservations.
    </p>
    <%= render 'garage_service' %> 
    <p>
      You are receiving this automated email because you are a driver in the LSA RideShare application.<br>
      <%= link_to "Unsubscribe", mailer_subscriptions_url %> from automated notifications.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
